                    <span>I have to say that if you want to get out of the rat race you need to understand how cash flow works.  This book will change the way you think about money - your money.  I couldn't recommend this book higher for everyone who is tired of working hard and tired of not being wealthy.  I also recommend Stop Working by Rohan Hall.  This book teaches you how to build a cash flow based Agile business.  Buy both of these books and learn how to become financially independent.</span>
                  
              
